   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Points that I can see (in FF 26.0 on Xubuntu 13.10):

- I think the top tab could benefit from moving down 1px so its border is not
overlapping the top bar (but IANAD :P).
- The &lt;hr&gt; in the left column needs a "clear: left;" so it doesn't sit up to the
right of the top tab.
- Firebug shows that "body ul.raquo_bullets{}" is being applied 5 times
(numbered #2 thru #6)??
- "body ul.raquo_bullets{ padding-left: 1.1em; }" puts the bullets inside the box.
- Or ".ui-widget-content{ padding-left: 0.9em }" does the same thing, and also
adds spacing to the text above them.</pre>
   </td>
